    "last_updated": "2026-06-09",
    "status": "draft_requirements",
    "purpose": "First engineering requirement draft for the most IO-sensitive IoTEdges models: IER-100, IER-140 and IEIO-100.",
    "important_note": "These requirements are intended for product planning and engineering discussion. They are not final datasheets and must be validated through schematic design, PCB layout, firmware implementation, prototype testing and compliance review."
